    Helper class used to wrap the boolean attributes that are passed to the Ant task in the Ant build script.

    Helper class used to wrap the File attributes that are passed to the Ant task in the Ant build script.

    Exception class used when an illegal attribute has been passed to the Ant task in the Ant build script.
